<style>
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 10%, rgba(42, 92, 145, 0.08), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f8fc 0%, #ffffff 48%, #f7f9fc 100%);
    color: #0c2340;
  }

  .materials-page {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 430px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 18px 18px 30px;
  }

  /* ===== 上部タイトル ===== */
  .materials-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 24px 22px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.13), transparent 30%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #071d3a 0%, #0b3765 58%, #39719e 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(7, 29, 58, 0.18);
  }

  .materials-hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 177, 82, 0.12);
    border-radius: 50%;
    right: -45px;
    top: -70px;
  }

  .materials-hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
    right: 20px;
    bottom: -65px;
  }

  .hero-top {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .hero-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 2px solid #d7b75c;
    border-radius: 15px;
    font-size: 25px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .hero-title {
    margin: 0;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: "Yu Mincho", "Hiragino Mincho ProN", serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .hero-en {
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: #d7b75c;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .hero-message {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin: 17px 0 0;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(215, 183, 92, 0.35);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    font-size: 10px;
    white-space: normal;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ===== 見出し ===== */
  .materials-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 11px;
    margin: 0 0 17px;
    font-family: "Yu Mincho", "Hiragino Mincho ProN", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #102b4c;
  }

  .materials-heading::before,
  .materials-heading::after {
    content: "";
    width: 38px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #c7a94d);
  }

  .materials-heading::after {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c7a94d, transparent);
  }

  /* ===== カード ===== */
  .materials-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 11px;
  }

  .material-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 70px;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 8px 48px 8px 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 48, 82, 0.10);
    border-radius: 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #10233d;
    box-shadow:
      0 7px 18px rgba(15, 48, 82, 0.07),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .material-card:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
  }

  .material-card::after {
    content: "›";
    position: absolute;
    right: 19px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-53%);
    color: #a7b0bb;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .material-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-right: 15px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .material-text {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .material-name {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Yu Mincho", "Hiragino Mincho ProN", serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .material-en {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 3px;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
  }

  /* ===== 分野カラー ===== */
  .bone-card {
    border-bottom: 4px solid #d4b13e;
  }

  .bone-card .material-icon {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #fff9dc, #efd26c);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(212,177,62,0.24);
  }

  .bone-card .material-en {
    color: #a98722;
  }

  .muscle-card {
    border-bottom: 4px solid #d69a32;
  }

  .muscle-card .material-icon {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #fff3d2, #efb95a);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(214,154,50,0.24);
  }

  .muscle-card .material-en {
    color: #b37817;
  }

  .neuro-card {
    border-bottom: 4px solid #a93c3c;
  }

  .neuro-card .material-icon {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #ffe3e3, #d86a6a);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(169,60,60,0.22);
  }

  .neuro-card .material-en {
    color: #a93c3c;
  }

  .physiology-card {
    border-bottom: 4px solid #d62f43;
  }

  .physiology-card .material-icon {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #ffdfe4, #ef6f7d);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(214,47,67,0.22);
  }

  .physiology-card .material-en {
    color: #c5293c;
  }

  .kinesiology-card {
    border-bottom: 4px solid #286dc5;
  }

  .kinesiology-card .material-icon {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #ddecff, #5597e8);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(40,109,197,0.22);
  }

  .kinesiology-card .material-en {
    color: #286dc5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .materials-page {
      padding-left: 14px;
      padding-right: 14px;
    }

    .materials-hero {
      padding-left: 18px;
      padding-right: 18px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .material-name {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="materials-page">

  <section class="materials-hero">
    <div class="hero-top">
      <div class="hero-icon">📚</div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">参考資料</h1>
        <div class="hero-en">REFERENCE LIBRARY</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="hero-message">
      国試対策に役立つ資料を分野別にまとめています。<br><br>
      💡国試ポイント・🧠覚え方（ゴロ）など、学習に役立つ内容を今後も継続的に追加・更新していきます。<br><br>
      📥 買い切り商品です。一度ご購入いただくと、今後追加・更新された最新版もご利用いただけます。
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="materials-heading">
    資料を選んでください
  </div>

  <div class="materials-list">

    <a href="/bone_pdfs" class="material-card bone-card">
      <div class="material-icon">🦴</div>
      <div class="material-text">
        <span class="material-name">骨資料集</span>
        <span class="material-en">BONE LIBRARY</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/muscle_pdfs" class="material-card muscle-card">
      <div class="material-icon">💪</div>
      <div class="material-text">
        <span class="material-name">筋肉資料集</span>
        <span class="material-en">MUSCLE LIBRARY</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/neurovascular_pdfs" class="material-card neuro-card">
      <div class="material-icon">🩸</div>
      <div class="material-text">
        <span class="material-name">神経・血管資料集</span>
        <span class="material-en">NEUROVASCULAR LIBRARY</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/physiology_pdfs" class="material-card physiology-card">
      <div class="material-icon">🫀</div>
      <div class="material-text">
        <span class="material-name">生理学資料集</span>
        <span class="material-en">PHYSIOLOGY LIBRARY</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/kinesiology_pdfs" class="material-card kinesiology-card">
      <div class="material-icon">🏃</div>
      <div class="material-text">
        <span class="material-name">運動学資料集</span>
        <span class="material-en">KINESIOLOGY LIBRARY</span>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>

</div>